eNCA's Barry Bateman has more details. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Two JMPD officials and a member of the public have been arrested for theft and illegally dealing with ammunition. READ: JMPD officers arrested following bribery accusations One of the officials arrested had 5,400 rounds of JMPD rifle ammunition in his possession. All three suspects are scheduled to appear in court this week. eNCA speaks to anti-crime activist Yusuf Abramjee. Courtesy #DStv403